  "prompt": "Which are the best CBSE schools in Hyderabad?",
  "response": "Hyderabad, the capital of Telangana, is home to several high-quality CBSE schools. Here are some of the best CBSE schools in Hyderabad:\n\n1. **Delhi Public School (DPS) Hyderabad**\n   - **Location:** Nacharam, Hyderabad\n   - **Highlights:** Known for its excellent academic record, modern infrastructure, and a wide range of extracurricular activities. DPS Hyderabad emphasizes holistic development and offers facilities like smart classrooms, well-equipped labs, and sports facilities.\n\n2. **Oakridge International School**\n   - **Location:** Gachibowli, Hyderabad\n   - **Highlights:** Oakridge offers both CBSE and IB curricula. It is renowned for its international standards, innovative teaching methods, and state-of-the-art facilities. The school focuses on fostering critical thinking, creativity, and global awareness.\n\n3. **Bharatiya Vidya Bhavan\u2019s Public School**\n   - **Location:** Jubilee Hills, Hyderabad\n   - **Highlights:** This school is known for its strong emphasis on Indian culture and values alongside a rigorous academic curriculum. It boasts well-equipped labs, a library, and various sports facilities. The school encourages participation in extracurricular activities and community service.\n\n4. **Army Public School**\n   - **Location:** Bolarum, Secunderabad\n   - **Highlights:** Catering primarily to the children of army personnel, this school is known for its disciplined environment and strong academic focus. It offers a wide range of facilities, including science labs, computer labs, and sports grounds.\n\n5. **Kendriya Vidyalaya (KV) - various locations**\n   - **Locations:** Multiple branches across Hyderabad, including KV Gachibowli, KV Picket, and KV Golconda.\n   - **Highlights:** Kendriya Vidyalayas are known for their consistent quality of education and affordability. They follow the CBSE curriculum and are preferred for their focus on all-around development and strong academic performance.\n\n6. **Glendale Academy**\n   - **Location:** Tolichowki, Hyderabad\n   - **Highlights:** Known for its balanced approach to academics and extracurriculars, Glendale Academy offers a nurturing environment with modern facilities. The school emphasizes on character building and holistic development.\n\n7. **P Obul Reddy Public School**\n   - **Location:** Jubilee Hills, Hyderabad\n   - **Highlights:** This school is renowned for its academic excellence and comprehensive facilities. It provides a stimulating learning environment and encourages students to participate in sports, arts, and other co-curricular activities.\n\nWhen choosing a school, consider factors such as the proximity to your home, the specific needs and interests of your child, the extracurricular programs offered, and the overall environment and reputation of the school. It's also beneficial to visit the schools, talk to other parents, and assess which institution aligns best with your expectations and values.",
